ing]]''\n*[[Deryck Guyler]] (1914\u20131999), ''[[Please Sir!]]'', ''[[Sykes (TV series)|Sykes]]''\n*[[Tony Hancock]] (1924\u20131968), ''[[Hancock's Half Hour]]''\n*[[Miranda Hart]] (born 1972), ''[[Miranda (TV series)|Miranda]]''\n*[[Nick Helm]], ''[[Uncle (TV series)|Uncle]]''\n*[[Jane Horrocks]] (born 1964), ''[[Absolutely Fabulous]]''\n*[[Karl Howman]] (born 1952), ''[[Brush Strokes]]''\n*[[Peter Howitt]] (born 1957), ''[[Bread (TV series)|Bread]]\n*[[John Inman]] (1935\u20132007), ''[[Are You Being Served]]''\n*[[David Jason]] (born 1940), ''[[Only Fools and Horses]]'', ''[[Open All Hours]]''\n*[[Danny John-Jules]] (born 1960), ''Red Dwarf''\n*[[Peter Kay]] (born 1973), ''[[Phoenix Nights]]'', ''[[Max and Paddy's Road to Nowhere]]''\n*[[Gorden Kaye]] (1941\u20132017), ''[['Allo 'Allo!]]''\n*[[Penelope Keith]] (born 1940), ''[[To the Manor Born]]''\n*[[John Laurie]] (1897\u20131980), ''[[Juno and the Paycock (film)|Juno and the Paycock]]'', ''Dad's Army''\n*[[John Le Mesurier]] (1912\u20131983), ''Dad's Army''\n*[[Helen Lederer]] (born 1954)\n*[[Robert Lindsay (actor)|Robert Lindsay]] (born 1949), ''[[Citizen Smith]]'', ''[[Nightingales (UK TV series)|Nightingales]]'', ''[[My Family]]''\n*[[Robert Llewellyn]] (born 1956), ''Red Dwarf''\n*[[Roger Lloyd-Pack]] (1944\u20132014), ''[[Only Fools and Horses]]'', ''[[The Vicar of Dibley]]''\n*[[Arthur Lowe]] (1915\u20131982), ''Dad's Army'', ''[[Bless Me Father]]''\n*[[Joanna Lumley]] (born 1947), ''Absolutely Fabulous''\n*[[Nicholas Lyndhurst]] (born 1961), ''[[Only Fools and Horses]]'', ''[[Butterflies (TV series)|Butterflies]]'', ''[[Goodnight Sweetheart (TV series)|Goodnight Sweetheart]]'\n*[[Rik Mayall]] (1958\u20132014), ''[[The Young Ones (TV series)|The Young Ones]]'', ''[[Bottom (TV series)|Bottom]]'', ''[[The New Statesman]]''\n*[[Greg McHugh]], ''[[Gary: Tank Commander]]'', ''[[Fresh Meat (TV series)|Fresh Meat]]''\n*[[Stephen Merchant]] (born 1974), ''The Office'', ''Extras''\n*[[David Mitchell (comedian)|