\n| opprank      =\n| oppseed      = 7 A\n| site_stadium = Georgia Dome\n| site_cityst  = Atlanta, Georgia\n| gamename     = Elite Eight\n| tv           =\n| score        = 66-63\n| overtime     =\n| attend       =\n| record       = 31&ndash;5\n| conference   =\n}}\n{{CBB schedule entry\n| date         = April 3, 2004\n| time         =\n| w/l          = l\n| nonconf      = yes\n| homecoming   =\n| away         =\n| neutral      = yes\n| rank         = 6\n| seed         = 1 A\n| opponent     = [[2003-04 Connecticut Huskies men's basketball team|Connecticut]]\n| opprank      = 7\n| oppseed      = 2 P\n| site_stadium = [[Alamodome]]\n| site_cityst  = [[San Antonio, Texas]]\n| gamename     = Final Four\n| tv           =\n| score        = 78-79\n| overtime     =\n| attend       =\n| record       = 31&ndash;6\n| conference   =\n}}\n{{CBB schedule end\n| rank =\n| poll = [[AP Poll]], A=[[Atlanta]] Regional, P=[[Phoenix]] Regional}}\n\n==Team players drafted into the NBA==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" width=\"00%\"\n|- align=\"center\"  style={{NCAA color cell|Duke Blue Devils}}\n| '''Round''' || '''Pick''' || '''Player''' || '''NBA Club''' \n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 1  || 7 ||Luol Deng ||Phoenix Suns*\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 2 || 38 ||Chris Duhon ||Chicago Bulls\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n|}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.databasebasketball.com/draft/draftyear.htm?yr=2004&lg=N |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2009-05-05 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100117120338/http://databasebasketball.com/draft/draftyear.htm?yr=2004&lg=n |archivedate=2010-01-17 }}</ref><nowiki>*</nowiki>Immediately traded to the [[Chicago Bulls]] through prior agreement\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Duke Blue Devils men's basketball navbox}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2003-04 Duke Blue Devils Men's Basketball Team}}\n[[Category:2003\u201304 Atlantic Coast Conference men's basketball season|Duke Blue Devils]]\n[[Category:Duke Blue Devils men's basketball 